Line1.2CDEB: Take the heart to the Druid, Yuein, at Túr Dúlra. Perhaps he’ll know if there is a way to deal with this magic.
Line3.2CDEB: I don’t recognize the magic that rotted my familiar. It is old, older than the Druids themselves. They could know of it.
Line5.2CDEB: He lived at Túr Dúlra before Astaroth's attack. If the demons that remain there are cleared, he’ll return.
